snippet.title: Starri Steam Release: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
➡️ Wishlist Starri on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1940410/Starri/

Starri is a body-controlled rhythm game you can play with just a webcam, no VR required. Feel your heart pumping as you slash or catch the beat, dodge obstacles, and turn the wheel. Engage your body with music from Indie classics, Global Top Hits and Asian lineups.

Get ready for new game scenes, outfits, characters, and songs coming your way with our Steam release this Fall!

Follow us on
🐦 Twitter: https://twitter.com/starrigame
📷 Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/starrigame/
👾 Discord: https://discord.gg/starri

#starri #movetomusic #rhythmgame
